---
title: Blueberry-BBQ Tofu with Roasted Potatoes and Spinach Salad
description: Sometimes the best things in life are unexpected—like this delicious combination of blueberry jam and BBQ sauce. This pairing adds a little something special to this tofu dinner, which is rounded out with roasted potatoes and a bright spring mix salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1015_W11_CA_RC155992-7_Main_low-85b2dd2b.jpg
